		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://aqualuxe.example.com/?page_id=3</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://aqualuxe.example.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/about-hero.jpg","id":128,"dimRatio":50,"overlayColor":"primary","minHeight":400,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full"} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-primary-background-color" style="min-height:400px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-primary-background-color has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-128" alt="About AquaLuxe" src="https://aqualuxe.example.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/about-hero.jpg" data-object-fit="cover"/><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1,"textColor":"white"} -->
<h1 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color">About AquaLuxe</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"white"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color">Bringing the ocean's beauty into your space since 2015</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"var:preset|spacing|60","right":"var:preset|spacing|40","bottom":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|40"},"margin":{"top":"0"}}},"backgroundColor":"background","layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull has-background-background-color has-background" style="margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)"><!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column {"width":"60%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:60%"><!-- wp:heading {"style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-x-large-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600">Our Story</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Founded in 2015 by marine biologist Dr. Sarah Chen, AquaLuxe began with a simple mission: to bring the beauty and tranquility of the ocean into homes and businesses through expertly designed and maintained aquariums.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>What started as a small consultation service has grown into a full-service aquarium design and maintenance company with a team of dedicated aquatic specialists, designers, and technicians. Our passion for marine life and commitment to sustainability drives everything we do.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Today, AquaLuxe is recognized as a leader in custom aquarium solutions, serving clients across the country with bespoke designs that transform spaces and create stunning focal points in homes, offices, restaurants, and hotels.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>"Our goal is not just to create beautiful aquariums, but to foster a deeper appreciation for marine ecosystems and promote conservation through education and sustainable practices."</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --><cite>Dr. Sarah Chen, Founder</cite></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"width":"40%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:40%"><!-- wp:image {"id":129,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->
